Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: django-adminutils
Version: 0.0.9
Summary: Utilities to make working with the Django admin nicer.
Home-page: https://github.com/GaretJax/django-adminutils
Author: Jonathan Stoppani
Author-email: jonathan@stoppani.name
License: MIT
Description: django-adminutils
        =================
        
        Utilities to make developing with the Django admin a better experience.
        
        
        Development
        -----------
        
        To release:
        
        * Ensure everything is committed.
        * Ensure the HISTORY.rst and the __init__.py files are up to date with
          information about the release.
        * Run `python setup.py publish`
        * Tag the release in git and push the tag: `git tag X.Y.Z && git push --tags`.
        
        
        =======
        History
        =======
        
        
        0.0.9 - 2020-09-09
        ==================
        
        * Replace ``load staticfiles`` with ``load static``.
        
        
        0.0.8 - 2020-03-25
        ==================
        
        * Make easy_thumbnails an optional dependency, again.
        
        
        0.0.7 - 2020-03-16
        ==================
        
        * Added a generic form processing action.
        * Add an option to not use forms to submit actions.
        * Compatibility with Django 2.
        
        
        0.0.6 - 2017-12-02
        ==================
        
        * Initial python 2 backport.
        
        
        0.0.5 - 2017-12-02
        ==================
        
        * Make easy_thumbnails an optional dependency.
        
        
        0.0.4 - 2017-11-23
        ==================
        
        * Fix manifest
        
        
        0.0.3 - 2017-11-23
        ==================
        
        * Initial release
        
